exports.data = [{"node":{"type":"update","timestamp":1590308570,"data":{"id":"RnJlZWZvcm1Qb3N0LTI4NDU2MDQ=","type":"FreeformPost","title":"Your Reward â€˜A work of Art by Quintenâ€™ has just been emailed to you!","publishedAt":1590308570,"pinnedAt":null,"number":22,"actions":{"read":true,"pin":false,"__typename":"PostActions"},"author":{"name":"Quinten","imageUrl":"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/027/201/370/9bb45615557ad6146d1d33b48ea336ec_original.jpg?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&w=160&h=160&fit=crop&v=1573658030&auto=format&frame=1&q=92&s=5c98839536071fb21f73b0ce262ee14a","__typename":"User"},"authorRole":"creator","isPublic":true,"likesCount":2,"commentsCount":0,"body":"<p><strong>This morning I have sent you your reward â€˜A work of Art by Quintenâ€™ by email.</strong></p>\n<p>Sometimes emails sent via MailChimp inadvertently get sent to the spam or trash box. If you havenâ€™t received the email Iâ€™ve just sent (Sunday 24th May just past 9:00 AM CET) go to your spam/trash box and find the email sent from Quinten-Art from email address <a href=\"mailto:info@quinten-art.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">info@quinten-art.com</a> with the subject: Download Your Quinten-Art.</p>\n<p>When you open the email you can then click â€˜<em>Report not spamâ€™</em>.</p>\n\n<div class=\"template asset\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt-text=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-id=\"29200389\">\n<figure>\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"fit\" src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/029/200/389/9e7c91a9d5a7c5a5aab602a1d36574ad_original.png?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=700&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1590308733&amp;gif-q=50&amp;lossless=true&amp;s=42f4f4666380758fcd1f6d03c2993064\">\n</figure>\n\n</div>\n\n\n<p>To <em>prevent future emails from ending up in the spam box </em>you can â€˜<em>whitelistâ€™</em> the email. Brilliant instructions on how to do this for Gmail, Yahoo and Outlook can be found <a href=\"https://support.appliedi.net/kb/how-to-whitelist-an-email-address-with-gmail-outlook_com-or-yahoo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">here</a>!</p>\n<p>If you still have problems receiving the emails just send us an email at <a href=\"mailto:info@quinten-art.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">info@quinten-art.com</a>.</p>\n<p>Via the email we will keep you updated about the <em>digital rewards</em>, new date of the <em>launch party</em> and <em>progress on the platform</em>. As an early supporter you will also get <em>exclusive offers</em> on the mugs or new products. So make sure your email is whitelisted!</p>","nativeImages":[],"__typename":"FreeformPost"},"__typename":"ProjectTimelineEvent"},"__typename":"ProjectTimelineEventEdge"},{"node":{"type":"update","timestamp":1588493238,"data":{"id":"RnJlZWZvcm1Qb3N0LTI4MjY3NzY=","type":"FreeformPost","title":"Important update!","publishedAt":1588493237,"pinnedAt":null,"number":21,"actions":{"read":true,"pin":false,"__typename":"PostActions"},"author":{"name":"Quinten","imageUrl":"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/027/201/370/9bb45615557ad6146d1d33b48ea336ec_original.jpg?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&w=160&h=160&fit=crop&v=1573658030&auto=format&frame=1&q=92&s=5c98839536071fb21f73b0ce262ee14a","__typename":"User"},"authorRole":"creator","isPublic":true,"likesCount":1,"commentsCount":0,"body":"<p><strong>Communication by email</strong></p>\n<p>To <em>deliver your digital rewards</em> and send you <em>updates about the project</em> I have just sent you an email via an email service provider (MailChimp).</p>\n<p>Sometimes emails sent via an email service provider inadvertently get sent to the spam or trash box. If you havenâ€™t received the email Iâ€™ve just sent (Sunday 3rd May around 10:00 CET) go to your spam/trash box and find the email sent from Quinten-Art from email address <a href=\"mailto:info@quinten-art.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">info@quinten-art.com</a> with the subject: Thank you for your support! The opening photo is a collage of people from all over the world who are happily showing off their mugs ðŸ˜Š.</p>\n<p>When you open the email in the spambox you can then click â€˜<em>Report not spamâ€™</em>.</p>\n\n<div class=\"template asset\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt-text=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-id=\"28942604\">\n<figure>\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"fit\" src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/028/942/604/9e7c91a9d5a7c5a5aab602a1d36574ad_original.png?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=700&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1588493144&amp;gif-q=50&amp;lossless=true&amp;s=85620e8a5de0665921a556cddfb0cbc3\">\n</figure>\n\n</div>\n\n\n<p>To <em>prevent future emails from ending up in the spam box </em>you can â€˜<em>whitelistâ€™</em> the email. Brilliant instructions on how to do this for Gmail, Yahoo and Outlook can be found <a href=\"https://support.appliedi.net/kb/how-to-whitelist-an-email-address-with-gmail-outlook_com-or-yahoo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">here</a>!</p>\n<p>If you still have problems receiving the emails just send us an email at <a href=\"mailto:info@quinten-art.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">info@quinten-art.com</a>.</p>\n<p>Via email we will keep you updated about the <em>digital rewards</em>, new date of the <em>launch party</em> and <em>progress on the platform</em>. As an early supporter you will also get <em>exclusive offers</em> on the mugs or new products. So make sure your email is whitelisted!</p>\n<p><strong>What if you havenâ€™t received your mug?</strong></p>\n<p>We have sent out all the mugs early April. If you have not received your mug(s), please send an email to <a href=\"mailto:info@quinten-art.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">info@quinten-art.com</a>.</p>","nativeImages":[],"__typename":"FreeformPost"},"__typename":"ProjectTimelineEvent"},"__typename":"ProjectTimelineEventEdge"},{"node":{"type":"update","timestamp":1585912896,"data":{"id":"RnJlZWZvcm1Qb3N0LTI4MDI3MzI=","type":"FreeformPost","title":"Mugs will be sent next week!","publishedAt":1585912896,"pinnedAt":null,"number":20,"actions":{"read":true,"pin":false,"__typename":"PostActions"},"author":{"name":"Quinten","imageUrl":"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/027/201/370/9bb45615557ad6146d1d33b48ea336ec_original.jpg?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&w=160&h=160&fit=crop&v=1573658030&auto=format&frame=1&q=92&s=5c98839536071fb21f73b0ce262ee14a","__typename":"User"},"authorRole":"creator","isPublic":true,"likesCount":3,"commentsCount":0,"body":"<p>We were awaiting the final 2 items that we needed to send out all the rewards (the reproductions and frames) and have just received news we can pick them up tomorrow!</p>\n<p>This means that next week we can start shipping out all the rewards!</p>\n<p>Note that the only reward we havenâ€™t been able to finish yet is the digital booklet â€˜Quintenâ€™s Journeyâ€™. The graphic designer who would help with this has been stranded in Asia due to the coronavirus outbreak.</p>\n<p>When she is safe and well again we will start making the booklet and send it digitally to all of you!</p>\n<p><strong>Some addresses still missing</strong></p>\n<p>12 backers have not filled out their reward survey yet. If you havenâ€™t done so yet, please do fill out the <strong>survey </strong>so we can send you your rewards. If your address has changed since you last filled out your survey, you can still edit your contact details.</p>\n<p>Note that we <em>cannot </em>send out the survey again. It can only be sent once, so please find your Kickstarter Reward Survey email.</p>\n<p>If you canâ€™t find the survey anymore or have any questions, just send an email to <a href=\"mailto:info@quinten-art.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">info@quinten-art.com</a>.</p>\n<p><strong>What if you would still like to participate?</strong></p>\n<p>Great news! You still can! This mug is a wonderful gift for yourself or others when working from home during lockdown. By buying a mug you'll also be doing good - 15% of the proceeds will be donated to the Autism Fund.</p>\n<p>You can still buy one (or more) on our webshop</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://shop.quinten-art.com/us/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">shop.quinten-art.com/us/</a></p>\n<p>Or you can contact us on <a href=\"mailto:info@quinten-art.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">info@quinten-art.com</a></p>","nativeImages":[],"__typename":"FreeformPost"},"__typename":"ProjectTimelineEvent"},"__typename":"ProjectTimelineEventEdge"},{"node":{"type":"update","timestamp":1585840772,"data":{"id":"RnJlZWZvcm1Qb3N0LTI4MDIwMDU=","type":"FreeformPost","title":"Support Autism on World Autism Day!","publishedAt":1585840772,"pinnedAt":null,"number":19,"actions":{"read":true,"pin":false,"__typename":"PostActions"},"author":{"name":"Quinten","imageUrl":"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/027/201/370/9bb45615557ad6146d1d33b48ea336ec_original.jpg?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&w=160&h=160&fit=crop&v=1573658030&auto=format&frame=1&q=92&s=5c98839536071fb21f73b0ce262ee14a","__typename":"User"},"authorRole":"creator","isPublic":true,"likesCount":2,"commentsCount":2,"body":"<p>Today is Word Autism Day. We are proud to announce that today our <a href=\"https://shop.quinten-art.com/nl/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">webshop </a>has gone live!</p>\n<p>What better way to support autism than to buy a Special Edition Tea Travel Mug made by a 9-year-old autistic boy with incredible talents.</p>\n<p>The mugs have been created to show the world the beautiful side of autism.</p>\n<p>15% of all orders will be donated to the Autism Fund (Autisme Fonds).</p>\n<p>Support People with Autism, because Autism can make Amazing Things Happen!</p>\n<p>https://shop.quinten-art.com/nl/</p>\n<p>#Quinten-Art #Autism</p>\n\n<div class=\"template asset\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt-text=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-id=\"28609727\">\n<figure>\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"fit\" src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/028/609/727/a59e72f15c1062994ac4d2eb54638a65_original.jpg?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=700&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1585840693&amp;gif-q=50&amp;q=92&amp;s=d5ad519a67f8be6b64c925030ccc3e6c\">\n</figure>\n\n</div>\n","nativeImages":[],"__typename":"FreeformPost"},"__typename":"ProjectTimelineEvent"},"__typename":"ProjectTimelineEventEdge"},{"node":{"type":"update","timestamp":1585493779,"data":{"id":"RnJlZWZvcm1Qb3N0LTI3OTgxOTk=","type":"FreeformPost","title":"The mugs have arrived!","publishedAt":1585493779,"pinnedAt":null,"number":18,"actions":{"read":true,"pin":false,"__typename":"PostActions"},"author":{"name":"Quinten","imageUrl":"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/027/201/370/9bb45615557ad6146d1d33b48ea336ec_original.jpg?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&w=160&h=160&fit=crop&v=1573658030&auto=format&frame=1&q=92&s=5c98839536071fb21f73b0ce262ee14a","__typename":"User"},"authorRole":"creator","isPublic":true,"likesCount":3,"commentsCount":0,"body":"<p>Finally some good news in these dire times. We are so happy because the mugs have finally arrived in Amsterdam!!</p>\n<div class=\"template asset\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt-text=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-id=\"28566520\">\n<figure>\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"fit\" src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/028/566/520/1d659032d3cd17aec72f48caa8c42c29_original.jpg?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=700&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1585493388&amp;gif-q=50&amp;q=92&amp;s=cfa6124e859e968f42da5bf14952a46b\">\n</figure>\n\n</div>\n\n<p>When we unpacked they were even more beautiful than expected. The packaging came out beautifully!</p>\n<div class=\"template asset\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt-text=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-id=\"28566563\">\n<figure>\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"fit\" src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/028/566/563/e9f37c3984e90441fe995c6393b6a650_original.jpg?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=700&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1585493714&amp;gif-q=50&amp;q=92&amp;s=d0ae0199d9210a1cc5d286e4ca484ec2\">\n</figure>\n\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"template asset\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt-text=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-id=\"28566529\">\n<figure>\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"fit\" src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/028/566/529/f7f5a486419abb9e3cc32609de626aff_original.jpg?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=700&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1585493457&amp;gif-q=50&amp;q=92&amp;s=e97d82ce3e5c2b42cec991e522f9250b\">\n</figure>\n\n</div>\n\n<p>Even the opening of the box was a delight. The print came out so well!</p>\n<div class=\"template asset\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt-text=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-id=\"28566532\">\n<figure>\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"fit\" src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/028/566/532/5ff45e3edf5003b66f91d5133207f6da_original.jpg?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=700&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1585493482&amp;gif-q=50&amp;q=92&amp;s=b072c93d510f7b4bced7b4f15f9262a0\">\n</figure>\n\n</div>\n\n<p>And the new strainer fits perfectly in the mug and is so much sturdier than the original sample.</p>\n<div class=\"template asset\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt-text=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-id=\"28566534\">\n<figure>\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"fit\" src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/028/566/534/3deb51396a8fa393bc7ecadb1468c430_original.jpg?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=700&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1585493505&amp;gif-q=50&amp;q=92&amp;s=ae3936bc6d5eb1be072d537e7fe9caee\">\n</figure>\n\n</div>\n\n<p>Of course we would like to send them as soon as possible but have been slowed down a bit due to the corona crisis. We are working hard to get everything ready for shipment.</p>\n<p>We are hopeful to be able to send the first parcels in the week of April 6.</p>\n<p><strong>Address information needed!</strong></p>\n<p>About 20 backers have not filled out their reward survey yet. If you havenâ€™t done so yet, please do fill out the <strong>survey </strong>so we can send you your rewards. If your address has changed since you last filled out your survey, you can still edit your contact details.</p>\n<p>Note that I <em>cannot </em>send out the survey again. It can only be sent once, so please find your Kickstarter Reward Survey email.</p>\n<p>If you canâ€™t find it or have any questions, just send an email to <a href=\"mailto:info@quinten-art.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">info@quinten-art.com</a>.</p>\n<p><strong>What if you would still like to participate?</strong></p>\n<p>Great news! You still can! This mug is a wonderful gift for yourself or others when working from home during lockdown. By buying a mug you'll also be doing good - 15% of the proceeds will be donated to the Autism Fund.Â </p>\n<div class=\"template asset\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt-text=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-id=\"28566557\">\n<figure>\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"fit\" src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/028/566/557/bf580786defb3e8fc77ddd20825d6fda_original.jpg?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=700&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1585493662&amp;gif-q=50&amp;q=92&amp;s=82a195fdd4266adc86c800fc441f29c7\">\n</figure>\n\n</div>\n\n<p>You can still buy one (or more) and support this project on Indiegogo by following the link below or by contacting me directly on <a href=\"mailto:info@quinten-art.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">info@quinten-art.com</a></p>\n<p>https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/quinten-art</p>","nativeImages":[],"__typename":"FreeformPost"},"__typename":"ProjectTimelineEvent"},"__typename":"ProjectTimelineEventEdge"},{"node":{"type":"update","timestamp":1584187069,"data":{"id":"RnJlZWZvcm1Qb3N0LTI3ODQ4MjM=","type":"FreeformPost","title":"Launch party 4th April postponed","publishedAt":1584187069,"pinnedAt":null,"number":17,"actions":{"read":true,"pin":false,"__typename":"PostActions"},"author":{"name":"Quinten","imageUrl":"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/027/201/370/9bb45615557ad6146d1d33b48ea336ec_original.jpg?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&w=160&h=160&fit=crop&v=1573658030&auto=format&frame=1&q=92&s=5c98839536071fb21f73b0ce262ee14a","__typename":"User"},"authorRole":"creator","isPublic":true,"likesCount":2,"commentsCount":0,"body":"<p>Due to the corona virus outbreak the launch party of the 4th of April has been postponed to a later date. In all likelihood the event will either be held in June or September. Of course we will keep you updated on any news.</p>\n<p>For all of you who have already bought the Special Edition Tea Travel Mug to celebrate the talents of children with autism there is also good news; the mugs are about to arrive in Amsterdam. This means that we will start shipping the mugs within the next couple of weeks.</p>\n<p>If you havenâ€™t done so yet, please do fill out the <strong>survey </strong>so we can send you your rewards. If you run into any trouble or have any questions, just send us an email: info@quinten-art.com</p>\n<p><strong>What if you would still like to participate?</strong></p>\n<p>Great news! You still can! For tea lovers the mug is the ultimate gift to yourself. But it is also a wonderful present to give away.</p>\n<p>You can still buy one (or more) and support this project by clicking on the link below or by contacting me directly on <a href=\"mailto:info@quinten-art.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">info@quinten-art.com</a></p>\n<p>With the money raised, we will build an online platform where children with autism can showcase their talents.</p>\n<p>https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/quinten-art</p>","nativeImages":[],"__typename":"FreeformPost"},"__typename":"ProjectTimelineEvent"},"__typename":"ProjectTimelineEventEdge"},{"node":{"type":"update","timestamp":1583669751,"data":{"id":"RnJlZWZvcm1Qb3N0LTI3Nzg4NTY=","type":"FreeformPost","title":"You are invited!","publishedAt":1583669751,"pinnedAt":null,"number":16,"actions":{"read":true,"pin":false,"__typename":"PostActions"},"author":{"name":"Quinten","imageUrl":"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/027/201/370/9bb45615557ad6146d1d33b48ea336ec_original.jpg?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&w=160&h=160&fit=crop&v=1573658030&auto=format&frame=1&q=92&s=5c98839536071fb21f73b0ce262ee14a","__typename":"User"},"authorRole":"creator","isPublic":true,"likesCount":2,"commentsCount":0,"body":"<p>On the <strong>4th of April</strong> we will organize a launch party to celebrate the incredible success of Quintenâ€™s Kickstarter campaign and to thank all the people who contributed to this success. We have an amazing line-up of speakers:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>\n<strong>Filemon Wesselink</strong> will tell an inspirational story about how he believes his autism helped him in his career</li>\n  <li>Stand-up comedian<strong> Fabian Franciscus</strong> will share funny anecdotes how having autism sometimes lands him in trouble</li>\n  <li>Documentary maker <strong>Monique Nolte</strong> (â€˜Het beste voor Â Keesâ€™ â€“ which was viewed 4 million times) will share her ideas about the importance of storytelling for social inclusion</li>\n</ul>\n<p>The event will be held at the beautiful location <a href=\"https://livezoku.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Zoku</a> in Amsterdam from <strong>14:45 - 17:30.</strong>Â </p>\n<p>Children are welcome! We will have a special play room for children with especially trained carers for children with special needs.</p>\n<div class=\"template asset\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt-text=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-id=\"28362074\">\n<figure>\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"fit\" src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/028/362/074/cd6d3b6ef2c37d7a5fcf725d1ad7d55b_original.jpg?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=700&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1583669565&amp;gif-q=50&amp;q=92&amp;s=4631b1e8c193860a7417364a4f6a8b87\">\n</figure>\n\n</div>\n\n\n<p>The <strong>NVA</strong> (Dutch Association for Autism) will be there to ceremoniously receive the first mug.</p>\n<p>The Quinten-Art launch party will be the celebratory conclusion of the Autism Awareness Week!</p>\n<p><strong>How do I sign up for the launch party?</strong></p>\n<p>Later today weâ€™ll send out the backer surveys. In the survey you can register for the launch party and let us know with how many people you would like to come by!</p>\n<p>If you run into any trouble or have any questions, just send us an email: info@quinten-art.com</p>\n<p><strong>Tell me more about the survey</strong></p>\n<p>The survey contains questions so we can deliver your rewards, so please take the time to fill out the information. It will only take a minute or so.</p>\n<p><strong>When will the mugs arrive?</strong></p>\n<p>The mugs will arrive in Amsterdam in March!</p>\n<p>Of course we will keep you updated about their arrival.</p>\n<p><strong>What if you would still like to participate?</strong></p>\n<p>Great news! You still can!</p>\n<p>We have opened a project page on <a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/quinten-art\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Indiegogo</a>.</p>\n<p>With the money raised, we will build an online platform where children with autism can showcase their talents.</p>","nativeImages":[],"__typename":"FreeformPost"},"__typename":"ProjectTimelineEvent"},"__typename":"ProjectTimelineEventEdge"},{"node":{"type":"update","timestamp":1581757912,"data":{"id":"RnJlZWZvcm1Qb3N0LTI3NTcyNDk=","type":"FreeformPost","title":"Save the Date!","publishedAt":1581757912,"pinnedAt":null,"number":15,"actions":{"read":true,"pin":false,"__typename":"PostActions"},"author":{"name":"Quinten","imageUrl":"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/027/201/370/9bb45615557ad6146d1d33b48ea336ec_original.jpg?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&w=160&h=160&fit=crop&v=1573658030&auto=format&frame=1&q=92&s=5c98839536071fb21f73b0ce262ee14a","__typename":"User"},"authorRole":"creator","isPublic":true,"likesCount":1,"commentsCount":0,"body":"<p>The preparations for Quintenâ€™s launch party are in full swing. It will have an amazing line-up of speakers and many surprises in store. The party will be held at the beautiful location <a href=\"https://livezoku.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Zoku</a> in Amsterdam.</p>\n<p>And we have a final date: <strong>Saturday 4th of April</strong> from 15:00 â€“ 17:00.</p>\n<p>The launch party will be the celebratory conclusion of the Autism Awareness Week!</p>\n<div class=\"template asset\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt-text=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-id=\"28102523\">\n<figure>\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"fit\" src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/028/102/523/cd6d3b6ef2c37d7a5fcf725d1ad7d55b_original.jpg?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=700&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1581757691&amp;gif-q=50&amp;q=92&amp;s=d3e4a58c7f23e86b207465472facf2c2\">\n</figure>\n\n</div>\n\n<p><strong>How do I sign up for the launch party?</strong></p>\n<p>Later today weâ€™ll send out the backer surveys. In the survey you can register for the launch party and let us know with how many people you would like to come by!</p>\n<p>If you run into any trouble or have any questions, just send us an email: info@quinten-art.com</p>\n<p><strong>Tell me more about the survey</strong></p>\n<p>The survey contains questions so we can deliver your rewards, so please take the time to fill out the information. It will only take a minute or so.</p>\n<p><strong>When will the mugs arrive?</strong></p>\n<p>The mugs will arrive in Amsterdam in March!</p>\n<p>Of course we will keep you updated about their arrival.</p>\n<p><strong>What if you would still like to participate?</strong></p>\n<p>Great news! You still can!</p>\n<p>We have opened a project page on <a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/quinten-art\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Indiegogo</a>.</p>\n<p>With the money raised, we will build an online platform where children with autism can showcase their talents.</p>","nativeImages":[],"__typename":"FreeformPost"},"__typename":"ProjectTimelineEvent"},"__typename":"ProjectTimelineEventEdge"},{"node":{"type":"update","timestamp":1580574894,"data":{"id":"RnJlZWZvcm1Qb3N0LTI3NDQ2MTU=","type":"FreeformPost","title":"WE DID IT!!!!!","publishedAt":1580574894,"pinnedAt":null,"number":14,"actions":{"read":true,"pin":false,"__typename":"PostActions"},"author":{"name":"Quinten","imageUrl":"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/027/201/370/9bb45615557ad6146d1d33b48ea336ec_original.jpg?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&w=160&h=160&fit=crop&v=1573658030&auto=format&frame=1&q=92&s=5c98839536071fb21f73b0ce262ee14a","__typename":"User"},"authorRole":"creator","isPublic":true,"likesCount":4,"commentsCount":0,"body":"<p>Rome is shaking on its foundationsâ€¦ and we are still recovering from shock, because <em><strong>we did it</strong></em>!</p>\n<div class=\"template asset\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt-text=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-id=\"27935066\">\n<figure>\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"fit\" src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/027/935/066/890aaed6fb4becb5823848a719380921_original.jpg?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=700&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1580574679&amp;gif-q=50&amp;q=92&amp;s=3a4816d9edf8e54d4819dc0fd5956ae7\">\n</figure>\n\n</div>\n\n<p>With your incredible help and generosity we were able to lift this project off the ground â€“ exceeding everyoneâ€™s expectations (especially my own)!</p>\n<p>Quinten was so happy he immediately took to the drawing table to expand his â€˜Star of Dimensionâ€™. He asked me to thank all the people by sending them this drawing.</p>\n<div class=\"template asset\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt-text=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-id=\"27935074\">\n<figure>\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"fit\" src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/027/935/074/16037f7da04caf7ca4aa925e2c9251ae_original.jpg?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=700&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1580574731&amp;gif-q=50&amp;q=92&amp;s=59c9b30b66be74a4e744aaeff46eb80b\">\n</figure>\n\n</div>\n\n<p><strong>Launch party!</strong></p>\n<p>To celebrate this incredible feat and to ceremoniously hand-over the first mug we will organize a launch party hosted by the incredibly funny Filemon Wesselink!</p>\n<p>The launch party will be held during Autism Awareness Week on either Sunday 29th of March or Wednesday 1st April.</p>\n<p>We will keep you informed!</p>\n<p><strong>Whatâ€™s next?</strong></p>\n<p>So what will happen next?</p>\n<p>Within the next weeks youâ€™ll get a <em>survey</em>. It would be great if you could help us along to fill out the questions! They also ask for your address so we can send you your rewards.</p>\n<p><strong>When will the mugs arrive?</strong></p>\n<p>If all goes to plan the mugs will arrive in Amsterdam on March 15th 2020.</p>\n<p><strong>What if you would still like to buy a mug (or know someone who will)?</strong></p>\n<p>Great news! You still can!</p>\n<p>We have opened a project page on <a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/quinten-art\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Indiegogo</a>. Here, successfully funded projects on other platforms can be continued until fulfillment.</p>\n<p>This means for the next 2 months you can still support our project HERE:</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/quinten-art\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/quinten-art</a></p>\n<p>With the money raised, we will build an online platform where children with autism can showcase their talents.</p>","nativeImages":[],"__typename":"FreeformPost"},"__typename":"ProjectTimelineEvent"},"__typename":"ProjectTimelineEventEdge"},{"node":{"type":"success","timestamp":1580488551,"data":{"goal":{"currency":"EUR","amount":"7500.0","__typename":"Money"},"pledged":{"currency":"EUR","amount":"9230.0","__typename":"Money"},"backersCount":166,"__typename":"Project"},"__typename":"ProjectTimelineEvent"},"__typename":"ProjectTimelineEventEdge"},{"node":{"type":"update","timestamp":1580452250,"data":{"id":"RnJlZWZvcm1Qb3N0LTI3NDMzODY=","type":"FreeformPost","title":"Last day of the campaign!","publishedAt":1580452250,"pinnedAt":null,"number":13,"actions":{"read":true,"pin":false,"__typename":"PostActions"},"author":{"name":"Quinten","imageUrl":"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/027/201/370/9bb45615557ad6146d1d33b48ea336ec_original.jpg?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&w=160&h=160&fit=crop&v=1573658030&auto=format&frame=1&q=92&s=5c98839536071fb21f73b0ce262ee14a","__typename":"User"},"authorRole":"creator","isPublic":true,"likesCount":4,"commentsCount":0,"body":"<p>Today is the very last day of Quintenâ€™s Kickstarter campaign!</p>\n<p>If you know of anyone who wants to participate but hasnâ€™t come around to it, now is the time ðŸ˜Š (until 5:35 PM today).</p>\n<p>You can share this link: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/quinten-art/quinten-art</p>\n<p>With the money raised, we will build an online platform where children with autism can showcase their talents.</p>\n<p>Yesterday Quinten was invited by the Escher Museum. When he came home that night he felt so inspired that he made this drawing he named: Star of Dimension</p>\n<div class=\"template asset\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt-text=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-id=\"27920319\">\n<figure>\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"fit\" src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/027/920/319/b8d6b255246a0f3e6c52ea41c98c1e15_original.jpg?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=700&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1580451872&amp;gif-q=50&amp;q=92&amp;s=065512b32cd030680192e64687b5a5cc\">\n</figure>\n\n</div>\n\n<p>For all of you have already donated I want to say a <em><strong>huge Thank You</strong></em>! This project has been a success thanks to your help and generosity.Â </p>\n<p>Your pledges have helped us create the mugs to raise awareness of the beautiful and often unseen talents children with autism have.Â </p>","nativeImages":[],"__typename":"FreeformPost"},"__typename":"ProjectTimelineEvent"},"__typename":"ProjectTimelineEventEdge"},{"node":{"type":"update","timestamp":1580030054,"data":{"id":"RnJlZWZvcm1Qb3N0LTI3MzkyMjA=","type":"FreeformPost","title":"Amazing news! Filemon Wesselink will host the launch party!!","publishedAt":1580030054,"pinnedAt":null,"number":12,"actions":{"read":true,"pin":false,"__typename":"PostActions"},"author":{"name":"Quinten","imageUrl":"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/027/201/370/9bb45615557ad6146d1d33b48ea336ec_original.jpg?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&w=160&h=160&fit=crop&v=1573658030&auto=format&frame=1&q=92&s=5c98839536071fb21f73b0ce262ee14a","__typename":"User"},"authorRole":"creator","isPublic":true,"likesCount":8,"commentsCount":0,"body":"<p>Big news today!<br>\n</p>\n<p>Filemon Wesselink will be hosting the launch party of Quintenâ€™s Kickstarter campaign!Â </p>\n<p>For those of you who donâ€™t know Filemon. He is a very charismatic Dutch TV personality, who was diagnosed with autism only a couple of years ago. Since then he has made numerous programs about autism to meet people like himself and to learn more about autism. He is incredibly funny and vulnerable at the same time.</p>\n<p>The launch party will be held during Autism Awareness Week between March 28th Â and April 4th at the breathtaking location Zoku in Amsterdam.</p>\n<p>And the party will have more surprises in store for you!</p>\n<p>To automatically get an invite to the party be sure to buy a mug in this final week of Quintenâ€™s Kickstarter campaign!</p>\n<p>You can buy your mug <a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/quinten-art/quinten-art\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">here</a></p>\n<p>With the money raised, we will build an online platform where children with autism across the globe can showcase their talents. Like this piece of art by Violet Reeves:</p>\n<div class=\"template asset\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt-text=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-id=\"27865425\">\n<figure>\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"fit\" src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/027/865/425/643ab9e04df3670211c1040d789a2f00_original.JPG?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=700&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1580030013&amp;gif-q=50&amp;q=92&amp;s=f3df96cbc8b7b19c27144910c49f9c6a\">\n</figure>\n\n</div>\n","nativeImages":[],"__typename":"FreeformPost"},"__typename":"ProjectTimelineEvent"},"__typename":"ProjectTimelineEventEdge"},{"node":{"type":"update","timestamp":1579347798,"data":{"id":"RnJlZWZvcm1Qb3N0LTI3MzM2OTM=","type":"FreeformPost","title":"What if you have no credit card?","publishedAt":1579347798,"pinnedAt":null,"number":11,"actions":{"read":true,"pin":false,"__typename":"PostActions"},"author":{"name":"Quinten","imageUrl":"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/027/201/370/9bb45615557ad6146d1d33b48ea336ec_original.jpg?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&w=160&h=160&fit=crop&v=1573658030&auto=format&frame=1&q=92&s=5c98839536071fb21f73b0ce262ee14a","__typename":"User"},"authorRole":"creator","isPublic":true,"likesCount":4,"commentsCount":0,"body":"<p>We have received several messages of people that want to support the project, but don't have a credit card.</p>\n<p>If you want to contribute, but don't have a credit card, please send an email to: info@quinten-art.com.Â </p>\n<p>On behalf of our family and all other families with autistic children, thank you so much for your support!!</p>\n<div class=\"template asset\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt-text=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-id=\"27789876\">\n<figure>\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"fit\" src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/027/789/876/91b4f4c55c873a1b937532d51408e2ee_original.JPG?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=700&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1579347643&amp;gif-q=50&amp;q=92&amp;s=223f6468df73b73f7b90b5f778b4b63c\">\n</figure>\n\n</div>\n","nativeImages":[],"__typename":"FreeformPost"},"__typename":"ProjectTimelineEvent"},"__typename":"ProjectTimelineEventEdge"},{"node":{"type":"update","timestamp":1578935011,"data":{"id":"RnJlZWZvcm1Qb3N0LTI3Mjk4NjM=","type":"FreeformPost","title":"Why raise awareness for the special gifts of children with autism?","publishedAt":1578935011,"pinnedAt":null,"number":10,"actions":{"read":true,"pin":false,"__typename":"PostActions"},"author":{"name":"Quinten","imageUrl":"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/027/201/370/9bb45615557ad6146d1d33b48ea336ec_original.jpg?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&w=160&h=160&fit=crop&v=1573658030&auto=format&frame=1&q=92&s=5c98839536071fb21f73b0ce262ee14a","__typename":"User"},"authorRole":"creator","isPublic":true,"likesCount":6,"commentsCount":0,"body":"<p>We are on our way to reaching our<em> stretch goal </em>- building a platform where children with autism can showcase their talent.</p>\n<p>Now why is this important, you may ask?</p>\n<p>National data indicates that the vast majority of adults with autism are either unemployed or underemployed, with estimates ranging to as high as 90%.</p>\n<p>Yet people with autism have unique talents that can be of tremendous benefit of the world. They can be good at tasks 'neurotypical' people will find difficult such as mathematics, coding, drawing or music.Â </p>\n<p>Our hope is that the world will become more accepting of people whose brains are wired differently. That, indeed <em>because </em>of this different wiring they offer us neurotypicals a unique view of the world.Â </p>\n<p>We also hope that the world will become a little more accommodating in creating environments where they can flourish.</p>\n<p>Setting up this platform is a first step in that direction. It is a place where we can see - and be amazed by - the incredible talents of children with autism so we can carve out a safe place in the world where they can flourish.</p>\n<p>So if you know anyone who would still like to contribute - feel free to share the link to this Kickstarter campaign!</p>\n<p>You want to learn more? My favorite introduction to autism for non-autistic audiences can be found <a href=\"https://youtu.be/RbwRrVw-CRo\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">here</a>.</p>","nativeImages":[],"__typename":"FreeformPost"},"__typename":"ProjectTimelineEvent"},"__typename":"ProjectTimelineEventEdge"},{"node":{"type":"update","timestamp":1578234127,"data":{"id":"RnJlZWZvcm1Qb3N0LTI3MjQyOTA=","type":"FreeformPost","title":"Production of the mugs started!","publishedAt":1578234127,"pinnedAt":null,"number":9,"actions":{"read":true,"pin":false,"__typename":"PostActions"},"author":{"name":"Quinten","imageUrl":"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/027/201/370/9bb45615557ad6146d1d33b48ea336ec_original.jpg?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&w=160&h=160&fit=crop&v=1573658030&auto=format&frame=1&q=92&s=5c98839536071fb21f73b0ce262ee14a","__typename":"User"},"authorRole":"creator","isPublic":true,"likesCount":11,"commentsCount":0,"body":"<p>First of all I want to wish you all the best for the coming year. Let the year ahead be the one where all your dreams come true!</p>\n<p>Our year couldnâ€™t start any better. Last week Quintenâ€™s Kickstarter project reached the threshold goal which meant we could give the order to start the production of the Special Edition Porcelain Travel Mugs:</p>\n<div class=\"template asset\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt-text=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-id=\"27659725\">\n<figure>\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"fit\" src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/027/659/725/260069f4c9381fa356657b0e5ca1a5db_original.jpg?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=700&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1578234092&amp;gif-q=50&amp;q=92&amp;s=20461fbb42474022bd1d1b9e44321518\">\n</figure>\n\n</div>\n\n<p>So far 250 mugs have been pledged. It would be FANTASTIC if you could help us find loving owners for the remaining 750 mugs that have been ordered. They will come in a beautiful gift box and will make wonderful gifts for your friends, colleagues, clients and other relations who would appreciate a one-of-a-kind gift!</p>\n<p>With the additional funding we will build an online platform where children with autism from all over the world can showcase their talents.</p>\n<p>Help support people with autism! Because autism can make amazing things happen.</p>","nativeImages":[],"__typename":"FreeformPost"},"__typename":"ProjectTimelineEvent"},"__typename":"ProjectTimelineEventEdge"},{"node":{"type":"update","timestamp":1577559635,"data":{"id":"RnJlZWZvcm1Qb3N0LTI3MTk3NjE=","type":"FreeformPost","title":"We've reached our threshold goal!","publishedAt":1577559635,"pinnedAt":null,"number":8,"actions":{"read":true,"pin":false,"__typename":"PostActions"},"author":{"name":"Quinten","imageUrl":"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/027/201/370/9bb45615557ad6146d1d33b48ea336ec_original.jpg?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&w=160&h=160&fit=crop&v=1573658030&auto=format&frame=1&q=92&s=5c98839536071fb21f73b0ce262ee14a","__typename":"User"},"authorRole":"creator","isPublic":true,"likesCount":10,"commentsCount":0,"body":"<p>An incredibly generous backer helped us reach our threshold goal this morning! We are over the moon with joy!</p>\n<p>We want to say <strong>A HUGE THANK YOU</strong> to all the backers of this project for your support and generosity.Â </p>\n<p>We are now adding a <em><strong>STRETCH GOAL</strong></em>.Â </p>\n<p>During these last couple of weeks we've been contacted by many parents of children with autism all over the world. They have already applied for their children to be part of the<strong> platform where children with autism can showcase their art</strong>.Â </p>\n<p>Pledges from new backers will go towards <strong>building this online platform</strong>.Â Â </p>\n<div class=\"template asset\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt-text=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-id=\"27604121\">\n<figure>\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"fit\" src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/027/604/121/1208c519581159692bbbc90b5afa8232_original.jpg?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=700&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1577559608&amp;gif-q=50&amp;q=92&amp;s=2aabfcdb24946a9522a3011b99e91d6f\">\n</figure>\n\n</div>\n\n\n<p>We would love your supportÂ </p>\n<p>in sharing this projectÂ </p>\n<p>so we can reach our stretch goal!</p>","nativeImages":[],"__typename":"FreeformPost"},"__typename":"ProjectTimelineEvent"},"__typename":"ProjectTimelineEventEdge"},{"node":{"type":"update","timestamp":1577092469,"data":{"id":"RnJlZWZvcm1Qb3N0LTI3MTY4MTA=","type":"FreeformPost","title":"Downloadable Voucher to gift Quinten's mug for Xmas","publishedAt":1577092469,"pinnedAt":null,"number":7,"actions":{"read":true,"pin":false,"__typename":"PostActions"},"author":{"name":"Quinten","imageUrl":"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/027/201/370/9bb45615557ad6146d1d33b48ea336ec_original.jpg?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&w=160&h=160&fit=crop&v=1573658030&auto=format&frame=1&q=92&s=5c98839536071fb21f73b0ce262ee14a","__typename":"User"},"authorRole":"creator","isPublic":true,"likesCount":6,"commentsCount":0,"body":"<p>Xmas is getting close! We've made a beautiful voucher which you can give as a Xmas gift in lieu of the actual Special Edition Tea Travel Mug.Â </p>\n<p>You can download the voucher <a href=\"https://carefreemom.ck.page/54cacece42\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">here</a>.Â </p>\n<p>For inspiration: the mugs were given as a Xmas present to all the teachers in Quinten's school. We had the vouchers printed and framed to make them look extra special:Â </p>\n<div class=\"template asset\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt-text=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-id=\"27571558\">\n<figure>\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"fit\" src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/027/571/558/50667e5f9b57ff4a5cf0a842bc369c8b_original.jpg?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=700&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1577092323&amp;gif-q=50&amp;q=92&amp;s=0a55d2928bb82d0f824cdf27499994cc\">\n</figure>\n\n</div>\n","nativeImages":[],"__typename":"FreeformPost"},"__typename":"ProjectTimelineEvent"},"__typename":"ProjectTimelineEventEdge"},{"node":{"type":"update","timestamp":1576780836,"data":{"id":"RnJlZWZvcm1Qb3N0LTI3MTQ2MzU=","type":"FreeformPost","title":"Design of the Box you will receive the Special Edition Porcelain Tea Mug in","publishedAt":1576780836,"pinnedAt":null,"number":6,"actions":{"read":true,"pin":false,"__typename":"PostActions"},"author":{"name":"Quinten","imageUrl":"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/027/201/370/9bb45615557ad6146d1d33b48ea336ec_original.jpg?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&w=160&h=160&fit=crop&v=1573658030&auto=format&frame=1&q=92&s=5c98839536071fb21f73b0ce262ee14a","__typename":"User"},"authorRole":"creator","isPublic":true,"likesCount":7,"commentsCount":0,"body":"<p>I have received a question today if the mug will come in a nice gift box. And I can tell you that it will!Â </p>\n<p>Here are pictures of the box and the design you will receive your Special Edition Porcelain Tea Mug in:</p>\n\n<div class=\"template asset\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt-text=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-id=\"27549099\">\n<figure>\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"fit\" src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/027/549/099/97fecdda4a1d0318cdb97199cb359dc1_original.JPG?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=700&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1576780748&amp;gif-q=50&amp;q=92&amp;s=0d64aaefdbce2f255f45336d9c27eadf\">\n</figure>\n\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"template asset\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt-text=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-id=\"27549113\">\n<figure>\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"fit\" src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/027/549/113/1b84799864566879ea2bf62cafb0eb2d_original.JPG?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=700&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1576780773&amp;gif-q=50&amp;q=92&amp;s=5f875f5d2c0afcb41f7c07aa0d5dce14\">\n</figure>\n\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"template asset\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt-text=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-id=\"27549120\">\n<figure>\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"fit\" src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/027/549/120/18d9b6e089c3b97885730f88e7d39854_original.JPG?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=700&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1576780791&amp;gif-q=50&amp;q=92&amp;s=4e5c02cec87fbe7d9622f7e087b9818a\">\n</figure>\n\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"template asset\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt-text=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-id=\"27549126\">\n<figure>\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"fit\" src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/027/549/126/03e0f9829da3fa6f18107db6e7369df5_original.JPG?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=700&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1576780811&amp;gif-q=50&amp;q=92&amp;s=ab3cddc52ff867487ec12be8cfa28f6d\">\n</figure>\n\n</div>\n","nativeImages":[],"__typename":"FreeformPost"},"__typename":"ProjectTimelineEvent"},"__typename":"ProjectTimelineEventEdge"},{"node":{"type":"update","timestamp":1576675390,"data":{"id":"RnJlZWZvcm1Qb3N0LTI3MTM0NzI=","type":"FreeformPost","title":"In the News!","publishedAt":1576675390,"pinnedAt":null,"number":5,"actions":{"read":true,"pin":false,"__typename":"PostActions"},"author":{"name":"Quinten","imageUrl":"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/027/201/370/9bb45615557ad6146d1d33b48ea336ec_original.jpg?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&w=160&h=160&fit=crop&v=1573658030&auto=format&frame=1&q=92&s=5c98839536071fb21f73b0ce262ee14a","__typename":"User"},"authorRole":"creator","isPublic":true,"likesCount":3,"commentsCount":0,"body":"<p>This week was so exhilarating! Two days ago a film crew from the local news station AT5 came by to shoot an item about Quinten's project! And only 1 day later it was already broadcast. You can see the result <a href=\"https://www.at5.nl/artikelen/198939/quinten-is-autistisch-en-kan-goed-tekenen-meer-aandacht-nodig-voor-positieve-kanten\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">here</a>.Â </p>\n<p>Ever since then the pledges have exploded with funding now at 88%! This is so incredible!</p>\n<p>And that's not the only thing that happened.</p>\n<p>Here is last week's news in <strong>pictures</strong></p>\n<div class=\"template asset\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt-text=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-id=\"27537758\">\n<figure>\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"fit\" src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/027/537/758/0b588f79d6133cc17f70ee882c83f386_original.JPG?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=700&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1576675119&amp;gif-q=50&amp;q=92&amp;s=3af61392d1dc088a92cec767e0597b69\">\n</figure>\n\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"template asset\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt-text=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-id=\"27537767\">\n<figure>\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"fit\" src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/027/537/767/eb939ce8665516d66a8e15f17dfc2519_original.JPG?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=700&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1576675140&amp;gif-q=50&amp;q=92&amp;s=a6192d276ae1e9a877fb5708a0778545\">\n</figure>\n\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"template asset\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt-text=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-id=\"27537771\">\n<figure>\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"fit\" src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/027/537/771/cca8794f1a98357ce17604c4a18c050c_original.JPG?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=700&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1576675164&amp;gif-q=50&amp;q=92&amp;s=a7b2e237d642f11af833a0d93895015d\">\n</figure>\n\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"template asset\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt-text=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-id=\"27537773\">\n<figure>\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"fit\" src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/027/537/773/c4686741edc708606bccb867f1751b92_original.JPG?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=700&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1576675179&amp;gif-q=50&amp;q=92&amp;s=135d86714972468e8b47f06593137b48\">\n</figure>\n\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"template asset\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt-text=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-id=\"27537775\">\n<figure>\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"fit\" src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/027/537/775/74c55d7b2e7fa06071a461bba5db2d0e_original.JPG?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=700&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1576675192&amp;gif-q=50&amp;q=92&amp;s=6c51557d04f73576cc961036e0f4e900\">\n</figure>\n\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"template asset\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt-text=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-id=\"27537780\">\n<figure>\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"fit\" src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/027/537/780/7610261f28775c58503208632af1a9dc_original.JPG?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=700&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1576675203&amp;gif-q=50&amp;q=92&amp;s=e1b14ac0affe386d9aa7bb090f39d0fc\">\n</figure>\n\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"template asset\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt-text=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-id=\"27537782\">\n<figure>\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"fit\" src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/027/537/782/3079a301f6f7a0d86fe235aebc3a058f_original.JPG?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=700&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1576675211&amp;gif-q=50&amp;q=92&amp;s=043d0ff68aa98e86b3877a9bc046d019\">\n</figure>\n\n</div>\n\n<p>Thank you so much for your overwhelming support!</p>\n<p>We are looking forward to next week!</p>","nativeImages":[],"__typename":"FreeformPost"},"__typename":"ProjectTimelineEvent"},"__typename":"ProjectTimelineEventEdge"},{"node":{"type":"update","timestamp":1575977618,"data":{"id":"RnJlZWZvcm1Qb3N0LTI3MDU1NTk=","type":"FreeformPost","title":"What a week!","publishedAt":1575977618,"pinnedAt":null,"number":4,"actions":{"read":true,"pin":false,"__typename":"PostActions"},"author":{"name":"Quinten","imageUrl":"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/027/201/370/9bb45615557ad6146d1d33b48ea336ec_original.jpg?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&w=160&h=160&fit=crop&v=1573658030&auto=format&frame=1&q=92&s=5c98839536071fb21f73b0ce262ee14a","__typename":"User"},"authorRole":"creator","isPublic":true,"likesCount":5,"commentsCount":0,"body":"<p>Exactly one week ago, when I pressed the button to launch the Kickstarter campaign, I felt absolutely terrified... Having never done a campaign like this before I had no idea what I was getting myself into and how people would react to this project.Â </p>\n<p>We are exactly one week into the campaign and I'm sitting in front of my laptop writing this message with tears in my eyes.Â </p>\n<p>People I hadn't heard from in a long time sent the most heartwarming messages and pledged their support.Â </p>\n<p>Last week's Facebook post went viral with 6,419 views of the post (compared to my 18 Facebook friends) and the post I've shared on LinkedIn last Sunday has been viewed 3,042 times. People are sharing the posts on their own social media. This is just amazing!</p>\n<div class=\"template asset\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt-text=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-id=\"27467757\">\n<figure>\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"fit\" src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/027/467/757/dc7f8f91b7d14bc2070d57f9d6f8eb91_original.jpg?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=700&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1575976834&amp;gif-q=50&amp;q=92&amp;s=17ce98f0ae4a0f45cb615e948be1a538\">\n</figure>\n\n</div>\n\n\n<p>Meanwhile we are trying hard to keep enough peace and quiet for Quinten, as December is always a difficult month.Â </p>\n<div class=\"template asset\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt-text=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-id=\"27467774\">\n<figure>\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"fit\" src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/027/467/774/79d96a590f6becb107848efa69248f4d_original.jpg?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=700&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1575976928&amp;gif-q=50&amp;q=92&amp;s=3ff806dab37cd990408c67b7d69e73c0\">\n</figure>\n\n</div>\n\n<p>This year he is doing better than previous years, as his passion for drawing helps him keep balance.Â </p>\n<p>Thank you so much for your support.Â </p>\n<p>And thank you for sharing the love.</p>","nativeImages":[],"__typename":"FreeformPost"},"__typename":"ProjectTimelineEvent"},"__typename":"ProjectTimelineEventEdge"},{"node":{"type":"update","timestamp":1575573213,"data":{"id":"RnJlZWZvcm1Qb3N0LTI3MDMzNzI=","type":"FreeformPost","title":"The Gift of Giving","publishedAt":1575573213,"pinnedAt":null,"number":3,"actions":{"read":true,"pin":false,"__typename":"PostActions"},"author":{"name":"Quinten","imageUrl":"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/027/201/370/9bb45615557ad6146d1d33b48ea336ec_original.jpg?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&w=160&h=160&fit=crop&v=1573658030&auto=format&frame=1&q=92&s=5c98839536071fb21f73b0ce262ee14a","__typename":"User"},"authorRole":"creator","isPublic":true,"likesCount":2,"commentsCount":0,"body":"<p>Today is Sinterklaas in The Netherlands, which is the Dutch version of Santaclaus. It's a day of celebration and gifts. And we've received so many gifts in the form of pledges and beautiful messages. Over EUR 3,000 - or 40% of the project - has now been funded!</p>\n<p>We have been preparing gifts as well...</p>\n<p>Today our designer made a beautiful poster which you can download to give to someone else. This way you can buy the mug as a Xmas present. Of course the mugs won't be ready yet, but you can download this beautifully designed voucher, frame it if you want to, and give it to a loved one.Â </p>\n<p>We'll share the link soon, but here is an image of poster:</p>\n<div class=\"template asset\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt-text=\"\" data-caption=\"Give Quinten's mug as a Xmas present with this beautifully designed voucher!\" data-id=\"27430827\">\n<figure>\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"fit\" src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/027/430/827/fc54c4095c8c090e19ece5025bdc6009_original.jpg?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=700&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1575572657&amp;gif-q=50&amp;q=92&amp;s=27cec85faa4b44dc2fc9118458924bc1\">\n<figcaption class=\"px2\">Give Quinten's mug as a Xmas present with this beautifully designed voucher!</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n</div>\n","nativeImages":[],"__typename":"FreeformPost"},"__typename":"ProjectTimelineEvent"},"__typename":"ProjectTimelineEventEdge"},{"node":{"type":"update","timestamp":1575492982,"data":{"id":"RnJlZWZvcm1Qb3N0LTI3MDI1MTY=","type":"FreeformPost","title":"Sharing is caring!","publishedAt":1575492982,"pinnedAt":null,"number":2,"actions":{"read":true,"pin":false,"__typename":"PostActions"},"author":{"name":"Quinten","imageUrl":"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/027/201/370/9bb45615557ad6146d1d33b48ea336ec_original.jpg?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&w=160&h=160&fit=crop&v=1573658030&auto=format&frame=1&q=92&s=5c98839536071fb21f73b0ce262ee14a","__typename":"User"},"authorRole":"creator","isPublic":true,"likesCount":4,"commentsCount":0,"body":"<p>Today has been another amazing day! EUR 750 has been pledged making the total EUR 2,496. And we are just on day 2!</p>\n<p>And we've been so incredibly lucky with all the help we've been getting. Two moms from Quinten's classmates offered their help and this morning we were having an inspiring brainstorm session! They advised us to have a sticker made that says 'sharing is caring' to put on the flyers so people will know how they can share the project. What a good idea!</p>\n<div class=\"template asset\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt-text=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-id=\"27422033\">\n<figure>\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"fit\" src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/027/422/033/87dcb915f4714670f44a6f1c1d146650_original.jpg?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=700&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1575492330&amp;gif-q=50&amp;q=92&amp;s=8500646c76c3f1ed0f7402ba51e8cd19\">\n</figure>\n\n</div>\n\n\n<p>The whole day the pledges were coming in and we received heartwarming comments.Â </p>\n<p>At Zoku, where the launch party will be held, they allowed me to put a poster, flyers and the sample mug on a piece of prime real estate (a table near the entrance). Immediately after I put it there I already saw a lady looking at it and taking a flyer with her.Â </p>\n<p>Then we heard that Soulstores was sharing the project:Â </p>\n<div class=\"template asset\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt-text=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-id=\"27422093\">\n<figure>\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"fit\" src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/027/422/093/1697f50484d28be364038655393fb9ec_original.JPG?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=700&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1575492796&amp;gif-q=50&amp;q=92&amp;s=f1c52a46294cdccafaa1e2fc599a92fb\">\n</figure>\n\n</div>\n\n<p>How lucky we are to be getting all this help.</p>\n<p>Everyone is sharing and everyone is caring.Â </p>\n<p>Thank you so much.</p>","nativeImages":[],"__typename":"FreeformPost"},"__typename":"ProjectTimelineEvent"},"__typename":"ProjectTimelineEventEdge"},{"node":{"type":"update","timestamp":1575400756,"data":{"id":"RnJlZWZvcm1Qb3N0LTI3MDEzMTM=","type":"FreeformPost","title":"We've had an incredible start!","publishedAt":1575400756,"pinnedAt":null,"number":1,"actions":{"read":true,"pin":false,"__typename":"PostActions"},"author":{"name":"Quinten","imageUrl":"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/027/201/370/9bb45615557ad6146d1d33b48ea336ec_original.jpg?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&w=160&h=160&fit=crop&v=1573658030&auto=format&frame=1&q=92&s=5c98839536071fb21f73b0ce262ee14a","__typename":"User"},"authorRole":"creator","isPublic":true,"likesCount":2,"commentsCount":1,"body":"<p>Thank you all so much! We've come so far in 1 day! EUR 1,731 was pledged and 23% of the project is already funded!</p>\n<p>Today was so exciting. After we launched this morning people were sharing their own posts of Quinten's project on their social media:</p>\n<div class=\"template asset\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt-text=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-id=\"27410496\">\n<figure>\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"fit\" src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/027/410/496/e5f461a054d553375b65269d49e240a1_original.JPG?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=700&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1575400085&amp;gif-q=50&amp;q=92&amp;s=5051df5fd19859832cc94644e4f48752\">\n</figure>\n\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"template asset\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt-text=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-id=\"27410521\">\n<figure>\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"fit\" src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/027/410/521/a0e5ddd714d3a9ef4f85de5cff9ec9e9_original.JPG?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=700&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1575400200&amp;gif-q=50&amp;q=92&amp;s=98520573ce6744b85057b04bfd20cb0e\">\n</figure>\n\n</div>\n\n<p>And we received pledges from people all over the world - even Mozambique and the US!!</p>\n<p>The flyers were distributed around Amsterdam</p>\n<div class=\"template asset\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt-text=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-id=\"27410531\">\n<figure>\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"fit\" src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/027/410/531/13af62333f6965425dc6841cb0acee27_original.jpg?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=700&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1575400278&amp;gif-q=50&amp;q=92&amp;s=f4e0495f15e06aba0a51c9142a16cb05\">\n</figure>\n\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"template asset\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt-text=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-id=\"27410534\">\n<figure>\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"fit\" src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/027/410/534/eeca56b473d24aad23e8c44625404366_original.jpg?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=700&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1575400302&amp;gif-q=50&amp;q=92&amp;s=03207d53b27daf889c9d670dc7597629\">\n</figure>\n\n</div>\n\n<p>All this excitement was a little bit too much for Quinten, so when I dropped him off at school this morning he immediately started working on his newest drawing to quiet his mind.</p>\n<div class=\"template asset\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt-text=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-id=\"27410477\">\n<figure>\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"fit\" src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/027/410/477/84f641c1cb80378f77a5feba6c9de37d_original.jpg?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=700&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1575399966&amp;gif-q=50&amp;q=92&amp;s=cba9df49c143991c6d4dd837d606d6cd\">\n</figure>\n\n</div>\n\n<p>We are already looking forward to day 2!</p>\n<p>We would love your support in making this project a reality. You can do so by becoming a backer!Â </p>\n<p>And by sharing the project with your friends!</p>","nativeImages":[],"__typename":"FreeformPost"},"__typename":"ProjectTimelineEvent"},"__typename":"ProjectTimelineEventEdge"},{"node":{"type":"launch","timestamp":1575304552,"data":{"goal":{"currency":"EUR","amount":"7500.0","__typename":"Money"},"pledged":{"currency":"EUR","amount":"9230.0","__typename":"Money"},"backersCount":166,"__typename":"Project"},"__typename":"ProjectTimelineEvent"},"__typename":"ProjectTimelineEventEdge"}]